Kent Sprouse acknowledged almost immediately after he was arrested more than a decade ago that he killed a police officer and another man outside a convenience store .
A jury decided in 2004 that he should be put to death and should be spared the death penalty .
Sprouse was convicted of the death of Ferris Police Officer Harry Marvin ` Marty ' Steinfeldt III , andcustomer Pedro Moreno in 2002 .